"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-20-duplantis-tebogo-headline-lausanne-diamond-league-first-post-olympic-meet\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"LAUSANNE,\\u00a0Switzerland\\u00a0(AFP)- Armand Duplantis and Letsile Tebogo headline a raft of Olympic champions who will descend on\\u00a0Lausanne\\u00a0for the first Diamond League meeting since the end of the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9845130566746735, \"rank\": 0.015728947572558643, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 122, \"end\": 130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletissima\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4918729573245156e-26, \"text\": \"Lausanne\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletissima\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletissima\"}, {\"begin\": 145, \"end\": 159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.30864060478492e-33, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some 18 current Olympic or world champions will be present in the Swiss city for Thursday's meet, coming just 12 days after the last of the track and field action at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 203, \"to\": 389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 269, \"end\": 274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9997706337544131, \"rank\": 0.00019230796880310102, \"text\": \"Swiss\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}, {\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Duplantis defended his gold in France's national stadium and improved his own world record to 6.25 metres.\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 422, \"end\": 428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998937145972416, \"rank\": 8.138460024409689e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In\\u00a0Lausanne, the Swede will take part in a City Event held on an esplanade bordering Lac Leman - better known in English as Lake Geneva - on Wednesday, 24 hours before the main fare at the Stade Olympique de la Pontaise.\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 502, \"end\": 510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletissima\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4918729573245156e-26, \"text\": \"Lausanne\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletissima\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletissima\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Duplantis will be up against American Sam Kendricks, the silver medallist in Paris, and also Renaud Lavillenie, the 2012 Olympic champion and former world record holder who failed to qualify for what would have been his home Games.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 750, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Americans\", \"score\": 0.7694257520239033, \"rank\": 0.29611994772297634, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 759, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kendricks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Kendricks\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kendricks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kendricks\"}, {\"begin\": 798, \"end\": 803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.26260607922686e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 814, \"end\": 831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renaud_Lavillenie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Renaud Lavillenie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renaud_Lavillenie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renaud_Lavillenie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's the only pole vault event next to a lake,\\\" Duplantis said.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love to have it scenic, fun, more like a show.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1069, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It suits us well.\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I jumped 6.10m in\\u00a0Lausanne\\u00a0last time and have felt well rested since Paris.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1106, \"end\": 1114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletissima\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4918729573245156e-26, \"text\": \"Lausanne\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletissima\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletissima\"}, {\"begin\": 1157, \"end\": 1162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.26260607922686e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think there are still some good jumps in my legs,\\\" said the US-born Swede, who left Paris the day after the event for a \\\"much-needed vacation with my girlfriend to chill as much as I could\\\".\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1252, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.26260607922686e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Botswana's Tebogo will race the 200m on Thursday, the event he won in Paris when he outstripped Noah Lyles.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1360, \"end\": 1368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7490549290804016, \"rank\": 0.33501557920134567, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1430, \"end\": 1435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.26260607922686e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1456, \"end\": 1466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Botswana's Letsile Tebogo  The American, a three-time world champion in the distance and the 100m winner in the French capital, has called time on his season.\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1469, \"end\": 1477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7490549290804016, \"rank\": 0.33501557920134567, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1500, \"end\": 1508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Americans\", \"score\": 0.7694257520239033, \"rank\": 0.29611994772297634, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 1581, \"end\": 1587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9821936838703538, \"rank\": 0.014183665748962068, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo will be up against Fred Kerley, the triple world champion (100m and relay) and 100m bronze medallist in Paris, and his US teammate Erriyon Knighton.\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1655, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fred Kerley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\"}, {\"begin\": 1740, \"end\": 1745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.26260607922686e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1755, \"end\": 1757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_natio