_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"American Cole Hocker stormed to an upset victory in Paris, outsprinting world champion Josh Kerr of Britain, American Yared Nuguse and Ingebrigtsen.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2652, \"end\": 2660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Americans\", \"score\": 0.7694257520239033, \"rank\": 0.29611994772297634, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 2704, \"end\": 2709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.26260607922686e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2739, \"end\": 2743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9999999956703505, \"rank\": 3.356982757424162e-09, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 2752, \"end\": 2759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9990235708712563, \"rank\": 0.00097738321966651, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 2761, \"end\": 2769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Americans\", \"score\": 0.7694257520239033, \"rank\": 0.29611994772297634, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 2770, \"end\": 2782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yared N